<L>__{interior heathrow terminal cafeteria day}
<A>__{the cafeteria is crowded and noisy. ramirez walks with his tray as if looking for a table. there is an open seat where jack and amos sit with their backs to each other at separate tables. ramirez crosses to jack. ramirez is still bald but his hair has grown out a bit.}
<C>__{ramirez}
<P>__{(loudly)}
<D>__{is this seat taken?}
