<D>__{this isn't the place for this conversation.}
<C>__{ramirez}
<P>__{(pissed off)}
<D>__{no rules, remember? i want to go home. you said yourself we can't move again till he leaves libya. you don't even know when that's gonna be. he might stay there another year for christ's sake.}
<C>__{jack}
<D>__{no he won't. he's gonna make a move and it'll be in europe just to stick it up the dst's nose. i'm gonna go and find out about our connecting flight.}
