<A>__{ramirez gets up casually. angle on amos he has heard everything that has gone down. angle on koj he waits, standing a few feet away and not by the phones as he was told. he watches ramirez. something doesn't jibe... passwords were not exchanged. he crosses to ramirez's side.}
